{"tid":1166431,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"讀唔成書嘅人係咪都好鐘意話讀書靠死背？","createTime":"2019-05-22T12:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T12:48:12.000Z","uid":105678,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c2f4fc4d7b22a12d3065b6b2bf1928ae6e5cd5e9","tid":1166431,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，前排同班中同出嚟食飯，我老死就拖住條女介紹畀大家，身材高瘦，都幾靚女。<br />\n<br />\n跟住都係食住飯講下近况吹下水，回憶下往事，氣氛都幾好。<br />\n<br />\n講講下咁啱提到以前中學嘅讀書史，我老死條女就講：「香港地讀書係靠死背架啦，讀完都唔理解啲concept架啦」、「如果我都肯死背一早入咗大學。」etc<br />\n<br />\n聽完佢嗡，大家都面矇矇，話哂係老死條女，又唔好意思串佢，搞到場面勁尷尬，唯有：「講得好」、「啱呀啱呀」咁吹奏下佢。<br />\n<br />\n我老死就扮撳手機聽唔到，仲係度：「咩呀？講到邊？」<br />\n<br />\n頭先諗翻起都覺得條女柒，估計依加應該畀我老死飛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319b8407539e082529993d77e0fb5f808669c50f","tid":1166431,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:08:21.000Z","msg":"就等同冇學歷既人話讀大學冇用一樣"},{"pid":"d392ddc2ff6bcd203dc23f6b9afec8495a98e6b2","tid":1166431,"uid":838,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"「如果我都肯死背一早入咗大學」<br />\n呢句真係輸咗個勢"},{"pid":"f968a995a6a0016371918d3dcaef449217be407e","tid":1166431,"uid":79403,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"三個層次啦<br />\n明concept+背小部分<br />\n死背marking將勤補拙<br />\n懶"},{"pid":"18fadd2446345ddcf6b64c58a889ac4fea98542b","tid":1166431,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:22:04.000Z","msg":"如果我肯XXX, 咁我XXX <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0379c773ccc552e87cbb6515a8df65128bee4d3f","tid":1166431,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T12:24:35.000Z","msg":"咁姐係肯死背都入到HKU？<br />\n差呢句未講出嘴咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc30ad839b993689408d97a18b06dee35bdf2d5","tid":1166431,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy